name: "From the ∞th floor, downwards"
description: "From the Infinite Floor, downwards" is Part 1 of a 3-part story that portrays someone spitting the beeswax dripping from a burning candle inside his head downwards from the ∞th floor. Will what pours out of his mouth ever reach the ones below? If it does, then he is not on the ∞th floor. And if this is the case, I hope the candle cools down before it burns those below.
